Feature: (Obliteration Charm)

    Removes things not wished to be seen again.

    Pronunciation: - 
    Seen/mentioned:
        Used by Hermione in Order of the Phoenix to remove the footprints that
        she, Harry, and Ron left in the snow. Also used in Deathly Hallows by
        Hermione to remove the footprints she and Harry leave behind them in
        the snow as they journey through Godric's Hollow.
    Suggested etymology: - 
    Notes:
        The above instances only reveal that the Obliteration Charm can remove
        footprints. There is no explanation as to what effect it can have on
        other things.